My friend Leah has been with the
same guy four different times.

1:10:06.440 --> 1:10:07.640
You're just not trying hard enough.

1:10:07.940 --> 1:10:08.940
I'm such an idiot. I can't
believe what an idiot I am.

1:10:09.140 --> 1:10:10.040
No, you know what, Mark.

1:10:10.540 --> 1:10:12.740
Do not divorce your wife!

1:10:14.040 --> 1:10:17.240
Will you please just do me a
solid and stay with Vanessa?

1:10:19.740 --> 1:10:20.540
You're so young.

1:10:21.240 --> 1:10:22.640
I'm not that young.
I'm sixteen.

1:10:22.640 --> 1:10:25.640
I'm old enough to know when
someone's acting like a total a-hole!

1:10:26.740 --> 1:10:27.740
Oh, and you know what,

1:10:28.840 --> 1:10:32.140
I bought another Sonic Youth album
and it sucks! It's just noise!

1:10:38.140 --> 1:10:39.340
Juno? What's going on?

1:10:40.940 --> 1:10:41.640
Nothing.

1:10:42.740 --> 1:10:43.440
Why are you crying?

1:10:44.540 --> 1:10:47.340
