allergic to fine home furnishings.

1:10:49.040 --> 1:10:49.840
What's the matter?

1:10:50.540 --> 1:10:51.640
What's the matter?

1:10:52.340 --> 1:10:54.840
She's just a little
hormonal. Right, Juno?

1:10:54.840 --> 1:10:56.440
It's part of the process.

1:11:00.840 --> 1:11:01.840
What did you do?

1:11:04.340 --> 1:11:05.240
I didn't do anything...

1:11:07.340 --> 1:11:08.240
Just...

1:11:12.940 --> 1:11:13.840
I've been thinking.

1:11:14.840 --> 1:11:17.540
- What?
- Just thinking if this is the right thing.

1:11:19.540 --> 1:11:20.440
What are you talking about?

1:11:22.640 --> 1:11:23.540
Just wondering if it's,

1:11:24.640 --> 1:11:25.440
Just wondering if we're ready.

1:11:27.040 --> 1:11:28.140
Yeah, we're ready.

1:11:28.540 --> 1:11:31.540
We're ready. We've read the
books, we've taken all the classes.

1:11:31.540 --> 1:11:33.440
We have a nursery that is completely...

1:11:33.940 --> 1:11:39.240
Vanessa, I know we're prepared.
I'm just wondering if... I'm ready.

1:11:44.640 --> 1:11:45.440
Wait a minute.

1:11:45.940 --> 1:11:49.040
Juno, don't listen to him.
He's just got cold feet.

1:11:49.540 --> 1:11:50.640
He's just being a guy.

1:11:50.940 --> 1:11:52.240
The books all say the same thing.

1:11:52.240 --> 1:11:54.240
A woman becomes a mother
when she gets pregnant.

1:11:54.640 --> 1:11:56.840
A man becomes a father
when he sees his baby.

1:11:58.340 --> 1:12:00.840
He's going to get there.

1:12:01.340 --> 1:12:02.140
It just happened so fast.

1:12:02.140 --> 1:12:05.240
We put the ad in the paper and I thought
it was gonna take months if at all and then,

1:12:05.840 --> 1:12:08.040
Two weeks later, she's on that couch.

1:12:08.540 --> 1:12:09.640
She answered our prayers.

1:12:09.940 --> 1:12:12.740
Ever since then it's
been like a ticking clock.

1:12:16.640 --> 1:12:18.140
What are you saying?

1:12:21.240 --> 1:12:22.840
That it feels a little like bad timing.

1:12:26.440 --> 1:12:28.440
What would be a good time for you, Mark?

1:12:30.640 --> 1:12:32.340
There's just some things
that I still want to do.

1:12:33.540 --> 1:12:34.740
Like what? Be a rock star?

1:12:36.240 --> 1:12:37.040
Don't mock me.

1:12:38.940 --> 1:12:39.940
I'm just saying that this is,

1:12:41.340 --> 1:12:42.640
This is something that's
never going to happen.

1:12:47.540 --> 1:12:48.440
Your shirt is stupid.

1:12:50.240 --> 1:12:51.040
Grow up.

1:12:51.840 --> 1:12:53.940
If I have to wait for
you to become Kurt Cobain,

1:12:53.940 --> 1:12:55.340
I'm never going to be a mother.

1:12:59.940 --> 1:13:01.140
I never said I'd be a good father.

1:15:57.540 --> 1:16:01.140
I called Gerta Rauss and she said
that she can represent both of us.

1:16:01.140 --> 1:16:03.240
It's called a "collaborative divorce. "

1:16:04.840 --> 1:16:06.240
It's all the rage right now, supposedly.

1:16:07.340 --> 1:16:08.940
And it would be pretty easy
because we don't have any children.

1:16:09.940 --> 1:16:11.140
Thanks for making the call, I guess.

1:16:19.340 --> 1:16:20.440
Have you found a place to stay yet?

1:16:21.340 --> 1:16:23.940
- Yeah, downtown.
- A hotel?

1:16:24.340 --> 1:16:26.440
No, it's not a hotel. It's a loft.

1:16:27.540 --> 1:16:28.640
Aren't you the cool guy?

1:16:34.840 --> 1:16:36.040
I wanted a baby so bad.

1:16:37.540 --> 1:16:38.640
I know.

1:16:58.840 --> 1:17:00.640
- It looks like a bill from
Jiffy-Lube. - It's for me.

1:17:43.440 --> 1:17:45.540
I never realize how much
I like being home unless

1:17:45.540 --> 1:17:47.740
I've been somewhere really
different for a while.

1:17:57.040 --> 1:17:57.940
Hey, Dad.

1:17:58.240 --> 1:17:59.540
Hey, big puffy version of Junebug.

1:18:01.140 --> 1:18:01.940
Where have you been?

1:18:02.240 --> 1:18:05.440
Dealing with things way
beyond my maturity level.

1:18:08.940 --> 1:18:09.940
Where is everybody?

1:18:10.640 --> 1:18:13.240
Bren took Liberty Bell to
her tot ice skating class.

1:18:14.740 --> 1:18:17.140
When will you guys learn
that tots can't ice skate?

1:18:19.240 --> 1:18:20.540
You're looking a little morose, honey.

1:18:21.440 --> 1:18:22.340
What's eating you?

1:18:31.040 --> 1:18:33.240
I'm just, like, losing
my faith with humanity.

1:18:34.440 --> 1:18:35.840
Can you narrow that down for me?

1:18:37.740 --> 1:18:38.540
I just...

1:18:38.940 --> 1:18:39.840
...wonder if...

1:18:41.540 --> 1:18:43.540
...two people can
stay together for good.

1:18:45.140 --> 1:18:46.040
You mean like couples?

1:18:46.440 --> 1:18:47.240
Yeah, like,

1:18:47.640 --> 1:18:48.740
People in love.

1:18:50.340 --> 1:18:52.540
Are you having boy trouble
'cause I gotta be honest;

1:18:52.540 --> 1:18:54.940
I don't really much approve of
you dating in your condition,

1:18:55.940 --> 1:18:57.340
That's kind of messed up.

1:18:57.440 --> 1:18:58.240
No, dad!

1:18:58.940 --> 1:18:59.840
I mean, that's pretty skanky.

1:19:00.140 --> 1:19:02.040
Isn't that what you girls
call it? Skanky? Skeevy?

1:19:02.140 --> 1:19:03.340
Please stop.

1:19:03.740 --> 1:19:04.540
Tore up from the floor up?

1:19:04.940 --> 1:19:06.940
That's not what it's about.

1:19:11.140 --> 1:19:17.540
I just need to know that it's possible that
two people can stay happy together forever.

1:19:19.140 --> 1:19:20.440
It's not easy, that's for sure.

1:19:21.740 --> 1:19:24.940
I don't have the best track
record in the world, I know, but,

1:19:26.240 --> 1:19:28.040
I've been with your
stepmother for ten years now,

1:19:29.140 --> 1:19:30.440
and I'm proud to say
that we're very happy.

1:19:32.840 --> 1:19:33.740
Look...

1:19:35.040 --> 1:19:36.040
...In my opinion...

1:19:36.840 --> 1:19:42.540
The best thing you can do is find a person
who loves you for exactly what you are.

1:19:44.440 --> 1:19:47.240
Good mood, bad mood, ugly, pretty,

1:19:48.140 --> 1:19:49.640
Handsome, what have you,

1:19:51.440 --> 1:19:53.740
the right person is still gonna
think the sun shines out of your ass.

1:19:57.740 --> 1:19:59.140
That's the kind of person
that's worth sticking with.

1:20:00.740 --> 1:20:01.340
Yeah.

1:20:05.740 --> 1:20:07.440
I think I've found that person.

1:20:08.540 --> 1:20:09.940
Yeah, sure you
have. Your old D-A-D!

1:20:11.840 --> 1:20:15.040
You know I'll always be there to love you, support
you, no matter what kind of pickle you're in.

1:20:16.940 --> 1:20:17.940
Obviously.

1:20:23.240 --> 1:20:24.140
Dad, I think I'm just gonna,

1:20:25.240 --> 1:20:26.640
shove out for a sec, but,

1:20:27.340 --> 1:20:28.640
I won't be home late.

1:20:29.240 --> 1:20:30.040
Okay.

1:20:31.440 --> 1:20:32.540
You were talking about me, right?

1:20:33.840 --> 1:20:34.540
Oh, yeah.

1:21:31.040 --> 1:21:32.140
Hi.

1:21:34.540 --> 1:21:37.040
Did you put like a hundred
things of tic tacs in my mailbox?

1:21:37.740 --> 1:21:39.040
Oh, yeah, that was me.

