all the time, you look at my face.

1:22:35.340 --> 1:22:40.940
And every time I see you, the
baby starts kicking super hard.

1:22:42.040 --> 1:22:43.140
It does?

1:22:55.840 --> 1:22:58.340
I think it's because my heart
starts pounding every time I see you.

1:22:59.840 --> 1:23:00.740
Mine too.

1:23:03.640 --> 1:23:05.340
That's all I could ask for.

1:23:08.840 --> 1:23:09.940
You're golden, man.

1:23:13.240 --> 1:23:14.840
Can we make out now?

