Dad, either I just peed my pants or...

1:24:05.140 --> 1:24:06.040
Or?

1:24:07.140 --> 1:24:08.840
Thundercats are go!

1:24:09.140 --> 1:24:09.940
All out, all out!

1:24:11.140 --> 1:24:12.140
