1:24:12.440 --> 1:24:13.940
What about the parking stickers?

1:24:14.140 --> 1:24:15.240
Have you got Liberty Bell?

1:24:15.440 --> 1:24:17.440
Oh, sweetie, sweetie!

1:24:21.340 --> 1:24:22.140
Here we go.

