- Wait, wait!
- Out of the way!

1:24:39.240 --> 1:24:40.540
- Don't do that.
- What?

1:24:40.940 --> 1:24:42.440
- That.
- But it's fun!

1:24:45.140 --> 1:24:46.940
Bren, when do I get that
friggin' Spinal Tap thing?

1:24:47.740 --> 1:24:50.240
It's called a spinal block, and
you can't have it yet, honey.

1:24:50.240 --> 1:24:52.140
The doctor said you're
not dilated enough.

1:24:52.540 --> 1:24:55.240
Come on! I have to wait
for it to get worse?

1:24:55.240 --> 1:24:57.940
Why can't I just have
the friggin' thing now?

1:24:58.540 --> 1:25:02.140
Honey, doctors are sadists who like to
play God and watch lesser people scream.

1:25:03.440 --> 1:25:04.240
Oh, shit.

1:25:04.940 --> 1:25:08.340
Excuse me! Can we give my kid
the damn spinal tap already?

1:25:38.040 --> 1:25:38.940
And then...

1:25:39.840 --> 1:25:41.240
...out of nowhere...

1:25:42.440 --> 1:25:43.240
...there it was...

1:25:44.940 --> 1:25:46.140
There he was.

1:25:53.240 --> 1:25:55.540
I decided not to call Bleeker to
tell him that I was having the baby.

1:25:56.240 --> 1:26:00.340
He had a big meet against Manteno and I
didn't want him to get all worried about me.

1:26:06.040 --> 1:26:07.140
But he figured it out anyway.

1:26:25.140 --> 1:26:26.840
Someday you'll be back here, honey.

1:26:29.540 --> 1:26:30.640
On your terms.

1:26:43.140 --> 1:26:44.140
Hey.

1:26:44.940 --> 1:26:46.940
Nice legs.

1:27:28.740 --> 1:27:30.340
Bleeker decided he didn't
want to see the baby.

1:27:32.340 --> 1:27:35.240
Neither did I, really.
He didn't feel like ours.

1:27:42.840 --> 1:27:44.440
I think he was always hers.

1:27:49.240 --> 1:27:50.640
Would you like to meet your son?

1:27:52.940 --> 1:27:54.940
I have a son?

1:28:23.040 --> 1:28:23.840
How do I look?

1:28:25.640 --> 1:28:26.540
Like a new mom.

1:28:27.340 --> 1:28:28.540
Scared shitless.

1:28:54.640 --> 1:28:56.140
It ended with a chair.

1:29:52.640 --> 1:29:58.340
As boyfriends go, Paulie Bleeker is totally
boss. He is the cheese to my macaroni.

1:30:00.740 --> 1:30:03.440
I know people are supposed to fall
in love before they reproduce, but,

1:30:04.640 --> 1:30:06.240
I guess normalcy's not really our style.

1:30:13.440 --> 1:30:14.140
Hey.

1:30:14.640 --> 1:30:15.840
Hey.

1:30:20.740 --> 1:30:21.540
Ready?

1:30:21.940 --> 1:30:23.140
Yeah.
